creator: Viszen
descriptionHtml:
Gaggle is your flying community where friends and fellow pilots can see where others are flying and even track their flights in real time. With Gaggle all your flights are recorded in high detail, allowing you to see a detailed summary of your flight with a rich replay feature for you to relive the experience. Paragliding, paramotor, and hang gliding pilots have all the flight information they need to do post flight analysis and to compare flights with friends.

Some of the functionality of Gaggle includes:
* Recording and keeping a log book of all your flights
* Detailed flight summary analysis
* Share your experience with a rich 3d replay visualization
* Sharing your live location between pilots
* Friends and family can follow you to get notified when you start flying in the future

Gaggle is still in early development and the future holds exciting features and possibilities.

title: Gaggle - Your Flying Community

creator: Viszen
descriptionHtml:
Gaggle is a free flight recorder for paramotor and paragliding pilots with a keen focus on the social aspect of our sport. Gaggle provides you with all the instruments you need to fly with confidence and it makes flying with friends fun. With Gaggle you can see your friends location in real time and after the flight you can view your recordings and even link your friends recordings to see your flights with in the 3D replay.

Features available in Gaggle include:
* Easy to use in-flight instruments including elevation, wind speed, and waypoint directions
* In flight audio cues with helpful information so you can enjoy the scenery without looking at a screen
* Record and keeping a history of your flights
* Create groups to share flights with your friends and get notified when your friends are flying
* Share your experience with a rich 3d replay visualisation
* Share and see the live location of other nearby pilots
* Create and fly pre-planned routes
* Export your flights to GPX and KML files
* Capture your wings and engines and keep track of which ones were used for your different flights

We have many more features planned se keep an eye out and check back regularly for the latest updates in Gaggle.

We would love to hear from you! As a community we need members just like you to help guide us in developing the next set of features. Tell us what you like, what you don’t like, and what ideas you have by giving us feedback.

By installing and using Gaggle you must agree to the Terms of Use (EULA) found on the play and the the one found here: https://flygaggle.com/#privacy-policy

title: Gaggle - Flight Recorder

creator: Viszen
descriptionHtml:
Gaggle is a flight recorder for paramotor and paragliding pilots that works great for groups of friends flying together. Gaggle has all the instruments you need to fly with confidence and it has real time location sharing so you can see where your friends are when flying in groups.

All your recordings are automatically saved to the cloud keeping an electronic log book of your flights. Flight hours for equipment is automatically logged and you can connect bluetooth devices like variometers as well. All your recordings can be replayed with a built in 3D visualiser.

Features available in Gaggle include:
* Easy to use in-flight instruments including altitude, elevation, wind speed, waypoints, climb rate, remaining fuel, and airspaces.
* Airspaces for most popular countries.
* In flight audio cues that will announce your altitude, wind direction, and more making it great to keep your phone in your pocket.
* Bluetooth support for external variometers.
* Electronic log book of all your flights including equipment logs.
* Groups that can be used to share flights with your friends. Groups will also notify others when you are flying.
* Easy sharing of your recordings using an image or a sharable link
* Share and see the live location of pilots nearby.
* Create and fly pre-planned routes.
* Export your flights to GPX and KML files.

descriptionHtml:
Experience the thrill of flight like never before with Gaggle, the premier flight recorder for paramotor and paragliding pilots. Whether you're flying solo or with a group of friends, Gaggle has all the tools you need to make the most of your time in the sky. With real-time location sharing, in-flight instruments, and an electronic logbook, Gaggle helps you stay connected and organized while you fly.

But that's not all - Gaggle also boasts a built-in 3D visualizer, making it easy to replay and share your recordings with others. And with Bluetooth support for external variometers and audio cues that announce important information while you fly, Gaggle is perfect for keeping your phone in your pocket.

Some of the features available in Gaggle include:

* Easy-to-use in-flight instruments, including altitude, elevation, wind speed, waypoints, climb rate, remaining fuel, and airspaces for popular countries.
* Electronic logbook of all your flights, including equipment logs.
* Groups to share flights and notifications with friends.
* In-flight messaging with group members.
* Sharing of recordings through images or sharable links.
* Live location sharing of nearby pilots.
* Pre-planned route creation and flight exporting to GPX and KML files.

descriptionHtml:
Experience effortless planning, navigation, recording, and sharing of all your paragliding (PG), paramotor (PPG), hang gliding (HG), and powered parachute (PPC) flights with Gaggle – the ultimate flight computer and aviation companion. With Gaggle, you'll enjoy:

* Live location tracking for you and your friends, so you always know where everyone is during flight.

* ADS-B airplane warnings to keep you informed of nearby aircraft during your flight.

Gaggle works on all your Apple devices, and all of your information – including your equipment, flight logs, and groups – is securely stored online. Gaggle also works great even when you're offline and out of data coverage.

Choose Gaggle and join the community of paragliding, paramotor, hang gliding, and powered parachute enthusiasts who are enjoying the ultimate flight computer and companion on their adventures.

descriptionHtml:
Harness the power of flight with the Gaggle app – your ultimate flight partner, ideal for planning, navigating, recording, and sharing your paragliding (PG), paramotor (PPG), hang gliding (HG), and powered parachute(PPC) flights. Here’s what you can expect with Gaggle:

1. Live location sharing: Avail real-time tracking for you and your fellow aviators, ensuring everyone is in the loop during flights.
2. Comprehensive flight data: Stay in the know with information about altitude, ground speed, wind direction, and airspaces that assist in avoiding restricted areas.
3. Audio cues: Experience seamless audio alerts providing crucial flight values and prominent details, reducing the need to constantly check your phone screen.
4. Precision for paramotors: Plan your flights efficiently with waypoints and fuel level indicators tailored for paramotor users.
5. Variometer and Thermal Assistant: Maximize your flight duration with an integrated variometer and useful thermal assistant.
6. Community and Profile Engagement: Connect and communicate with fellow pilots via an engaging Community Section, featuring profiles for each pilot to share their stats, recent flights, and to privately chat with other pilots.
7. Organized Route Planning: Benefit from an intuitive planner that simplifies route planning and sharing with friends. Organize your routes into neat folders for easy accessibility.
8. Automated flight log book: Treasure every flight with an automated electronic logbook, capturing all your flights, flying hours, and personal best moments.
9. 3D flight visualizer: Relive every adventure with a 3D flight visualizer and share those unforgettable moments with friends.
10. Aircraft warnings: Stay aware of nearby aircraft through instant ADS-B airplane warnings for maintaining safe distances.
11. Flying sites: Discover new places to fly and see detailed weather forecasts for your favorite flying sites.
12. Groups: Effortlessly share your flights and adventures with your friends and family.

Gaggle securely maintains your data online, including your equipment details, flight logs, and group interactions. What's more, Gaggle runs smoothly even offline, out of data coverage.

Choose Gaggle as your trusted co-pilot and join the global community of paragliding, paramotor, hang gliding, and powered parachute enthusiasts. Embark on your memorable flight adventures with the best suitable partner onboard.
